    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Describes the practice of creating text, images, or code that has been structured, edited, refined, or improved by artificial intelligence. If text or images are created initially by human intelligence, and subsequently processed by AI, this would be considered 'AI-assistance.' For the process of creating content solely by artificial intelligence based on existing information, with minimal human input, use ‘AI-generation,’ even if substantial edits are applied after the process of generation of the primary content.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
